channel.title: InsidiaX Help! its urgent please help! (PI)
channel.description:
Ok so this message pops up in the chatbox every 60 secs or so and its saying "[insidia News]register online at www.insidia.com" ect, i wanna know where to change them
also
Im making a new home but im stuck, i cant get rid of objects for example tables and chairs where do i remove these
also
How do i move objects such as Chests or pray altars and how do i know there exact location to move them?
also
this is a little hard to explain, but theres this message on the actual screen when you first log in where you have to click it to get rid of it how do i change what this says..?
Thanks for the help to who ever can supply me with this information.
